{"tid":2074864,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇清試過收到唔知邊間公司電話話收到你CV in Marketing Assistant？","createTime":"2020-06-22T12:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T14:53:50.000Z","uid":96501,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6a5fe03326451ce5f001fe2f2e688d91f9e0fdff","tid":2074864,"uid":96501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:10:32.000Z","msg":"有間公司唔知係邊拎到我「CV」，就打嚟話請Marketing Assistant，<br />\n實情我根本唔係做呢行，而呢間嘢已經煩咗我四年幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說小弟係啱啱嗰個星期六又收到呢間鬼公司電話，<br />\n每次打嚟對白都喺：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你好啊 X先生 請問你喺唔喺仲搵緊工㗎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係，請問邊位？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我哋係萬寶公司（次次唔同），而家請緊Marketing Assistant，主要工作就喺市場推廣及分析，市場調查 blah blah blah，想約返X先生你上嚟Interview，你下星期X上奏方唔方便？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我做開Admin㗎喎，你邊度拎到我個人資料？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：哦........... 其實我哋公司都有請Admin Assistant（我試過話自己做Engin佢都話有Opening<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），都想見個面瞭解下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：（cut線...）<br />\n<br />\n你呃FG就得姐，出嚟做過幾年嘢都知係鬼公司（肯肯定係保險），<br />\n有冇Ching都收過？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966270944f1c8cea573aac438bc84f24c0c26410","tid":2074864,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:11:49.000Z","msg":"唔怕失業啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62340ea1ab9349542436184cbe64c9429e3